A middle school principal and his guidance counselor pal who produced sexually charged slasher pics have been put on administrative leave by their schools. 

Dr. Mark Foley, a principal at Granby Memorial Middle School in Granby, Connecticut, and Aaron Vnuk, a seventh-grade guidance counselor at Windsor's Sage Park Middle School in Windsor, Connecticut, not only produced horror movies with nude scenes, but also ran a website that included images of scantily clad women.

Among the titles produced by the duo were Mind Morgue, The Limb Collector, Demon of Castlebury, and The Bard of Blood.

